        <h3>About the Event</h3>
        <p>Robosoccer is an exciting robotic football (soccer) competition where participants design, build, and control their robots to compete in a fast-paced soccer match. Teams will battle in multiple rounds to showcase their robotic skills, strategy, and teamwork.</p>

